{"tid":2130992,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 熱狗用咩理由拒絕戴口罩？（患病/殘疾/困擾/避免受傷害）","createTime":"2020-07-29T13:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T08:24:48.000Z","uid":7439,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a4fbafb2ade58abf90c7c6afd655ca5780e02d9a","tid":2130992,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:50:29.000Z","msg":"原來係乖乖戴返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/115901838_1577338769107141_2517368242573556014_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=Al0LfuY8FTcAX__dLvx&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=1ab78534b2ae2ebc990b44061b85c307&amp;oe=5F47D26F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F115901838_1577338769107141_2517368242573556014_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DAl0LfuY8FTcAX__dLvx%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3D1ab78534b2ae2ebc990b44061b85c307%26oe%3D5F47D26F&h=51dae298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/116428070_3237765072952131_9218321710642174314_o.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=en2S3d4B6uwAX9KwK3q&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=4b42d937232dd80d04ad951da2ea9cf5&amp;oe=5F48A55D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F116428070_3237765072952131_9218321710642174314_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3Den2S3d4B6uwAX9KwK3q%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3D4b42d937232dd80d04ad951da2ea9cf5%26oe%3D5F48A55D&h=818b9399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/115936149_1188638861493520_656957678417796819_o.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=DOdaHNhYdG0AX94GGhF&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=fb23841f17e1d17fdf836e1439fe24af&amp;oe=5F47C7AD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F115936149_1188638861493520_656957678417796819_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DDOdaHNhYdG0AX94GGhF%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3Dfb23841f17e1d17fdf836e1439fe24af%26oe%3D5F47C7AD&h=a946516a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1b748e93e3d0d10ab84eba62e1cb6646248fbdf","tid":2130992,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:50:56.000Z","msg":"<em>在以下情況下，任何人即屬有合理辯解 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)以下情況 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(i)該人<span class=\"red\">因身體上或精神上的疾病、損害或殘疾</span>，而不能戴上、佩戴或除下口罩；或<br />\n(ii)該人戴上、佩戴或除下口罩，<span class=\"red\">會對該人帶來嚴重困擾</span>；<br />\n(b)該人正陪同或協助另一人，而該另一人依賴讀唇與該人溝通；<br />\n(c)該人有合理必要不佩戴口罩，<span class=\"red\">以避免自己或其他人身體受傷害</span>；<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(d)該人有合理必要登上公共交通工具或身處公共交通工具上，或進入或身處港鐵已付車費區域，以避免自己身體受傷害，但該人沒有口罩；</em>"},{"pid":"c1988e8ddbdf5897f0ced207a8e8e6cfab64c0c7","tid":2130992,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:51:12.000Z","msg":"熱狗係咪已經放棄戴口罩？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fEgwLS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fEgwLS</a><br />\n<br />\n熱狗：唔好出街呀，躲喺屋企啦。你仲要成日戴罩呀，訓教沖涼都要戴呀，唔係既話會被感染架，增加香港醫療負擔架。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2098271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2098271</a><br />\n<br />\n啲熱狗係威係勢呢兩日去到沙田咪又係帶返口罩。。。。。。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2099363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2099363</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰談国歌法：我曾在北京生活5年，博士學位在北大取得，論黨的語言比謝偉俊更熟悉<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fHCspS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fHCspS</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰不點名針對有區議員躲在天橋協助警察捉拿非法賽車<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2115237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2115237</a>"},{"pid":"aab84c03e66da5a9f8093f81279929cf0469a7a0","tid":2130992,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:52:32.000Z","msg":"蟈屍可以用a(i)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b23b3e8e6be9a7f2c7314f2df6b93b5d3c0c3a","tid":2130992,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:53:02.000Z","msg":"搵唔到法子戴罩相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(不過今日冇update<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/116042576_144147000643490_5340786618210550148_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=Tt23Dlb3H3AAX_mFzNh&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=95be900b62d35e88b217c45cdfe59602&amp;oe=5F47F508\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F116042576_144147000643490_5340786618210550148_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DTt23Dlb3H3AAX_mFzNh%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D95be900b62d35e88b217c45cdfe59602%26oe%3D5F47F508&h=7a98c8e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"925f5e1091523a6ff7699e9a44169c6f0141fda5","tid":2130992,"uid":100570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:54:02.000Z","msg":"四眼弱能都冇得豁免？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431969ba1ab92cbe28304f94756c4eee247995b8","tid":2130992,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:54:45.000Z","msg":"最關心選舉的屌票党<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>我們三區候選人簡單討論後，決定維持原定的街站宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n原因有二：<br />\n<br />\n一、即使不是選舉年，我們是要推動復興本土社區經濟、要求推出第三輪防疫基金、重組警隊制裁警暴、倡議區域法院設有陪審員制度等政策倡議。推動這些議題是出於現實需要，為香港所需、為市民所急；<br />\n<br />\n二、我們已製作不少傳單及宣傳品，為熱血支持者及一眾同道的支持，每一張傳單都代表大家對我們的信任，我們會好好珍惜。這是尊重及承諾。<br />\n<br />\n只是礙於明天生效的二人限聚令，我們會稍作調整。待官方公佈後，我們會再次正式答謝大家。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4e6196f26b28d8a3d4ee3cfc84a6a456b7bffdab","tid":2130992,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"925f5e1091523a6ff7699e9a44169c6f0141fda5","tid":2130992,"uid":100570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:54:02.000Z","msg":"四眼弱能都冇得豁免？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d0ba354cc11624326f2f2ff4e87a51c1db7e47","tid":2130992,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"925f5e1091523a6ff7699e9a44169c6f0141fda5","tid":2130992,"uid":100570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:54:02.000Z","msg":"四眼弱能都冇得豁免？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:55:20.000Z","msg":"法子先係排第一，港島主任(黃兆鍵老豆)問爬第二嘅牙滿做乜...........<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2125938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2125938</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ede7d5034a972273d5df6a55f5a4f90e1a345b","tid":2130992,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:56:15.000Z","msg":"啲短褲女又唔見晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/110171926_1190379794652760_8851552587343389721_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=M9I0h